1. "Selling Expenses" - costs directly related to selling products/services, including marketing, sales commissions, etc.
2. "Cost of Goods Sold" - costs directly associated with producing goods or delivering services

Looking at the income statement provided, I can see:
- Selling Expenses: 404114.07
- Cost of Goods Sold: 6720000.00
